0:00:00.000,0:00:05.360
Munhandare yerusununguko, ma wise men vari kushandiswa sematemo ehondo mumaoko aMwari,

0:00:05.360,0:00:09.100
kutema cheni dze madhimoni dzakaisa vanhu muuranda,

0:00:09.100,0:00:12.260
vachivasunungura pavanotaura zita ra Jesu.

0:00:12.260,0:00:15.040
Jesu ndiye ega Muponesi we vatadzi.

0:00:15.040,0:00:20.060
Zvauri kutarisa ndezvokwadi chekuti Jesu anorarama uye haana kumboti "chisarayi".

0:00:20.060,0:00:24.980
Tarisa kuna Wise Man Daniel apo anofamba achienda mumutsetse uyu, uye zvinoitwa nemurume wechiduku uyu,

0:00:24.980,0:00:26.960
apo anosangana na Wise Man.

0:00:26.960,0:00:31.280
Haadi kutarisa chiso cha Wise Man, uye ava nekusangadzikana pakarepo,

0:00:31.280,0:00:35.660
apo Mweya Mutsvene ari kushanda achifumura rima muhupenyu hwake.

0:00:35.660,0:00:39.240
Moto, muzita guru ra Jesu!

0:00:39.240,0:00:40.760
Moto, muzita guru ra Jesu Kristu!

0:00:40.760,0:00:42.860
Sei uri kubata vhoiri?

0:00:42.860,0:00:45.400
Ndiwe ani?

0:00:45.400,0:00:48.740
Usabata vhoiri.

0:00:48.740,0:00:50.880
Moto! Buda uye utaure iwe dhimoni!

0:00:50.880,0:00:52.300
Taura, iwe ndiwe ani ??

0:00:52.300,0:00:54.260
Ndati ndini Morpheus!

0:00:54.260,0:00:58.720
Uye ndiani umwe kunze kwa Morpheus?

0:00:58.720,0:00:59.620
Leo!

0:00:59.620,0:01:02.740
Musiye!

0:01:02.740,0:01:04.280
Ungagona here kusvinudza meso ako? Unoziva here kuti uripi?

0:01:04.280,0:01:07.520
Vhura maziso ako! Taura ikozvino kwauri! Vhura maziso ako!

0:01:07.520,0:01:10.600
Simuka utaure, iwe dhimoni.

0:01:10.600,0:01:11.700
Simuka!

0:01:11.700,0:01:15.240
Iwe unoda kuti mukomana uyu aparadze pasi rose?

0:01:15.240,0:01:23.280
Aiwa - kwete izvo tenzi wedu akawana.

0:01:23.280,0:01:25.820
Iwe wati uri Morpheus?

0:01:25.820,0:01:26.320
Hongu

0:01:26.320,0:01:28.000
Ndiani munhu anotevera?

0:01:28.000,0:01:33.100
Leo. Ndiri katsi huru.

0:01:33.100,0:01:34.280
Iwe uri katsi huru?

0:01:34.280,0:01:35.120
Shumba.

0:01:35.120,0:01:37.360
Shumba.

0:01:37.360,0:01:39.420
Ndianizve zvakare?

0:01:39.420,0:01:41.040
Ndati Adder.

0:01:41.040,0:01:43.260
Adder?

0:01:43.260,0:01:45.560
Ihama yenyoka.

0:01:45.560,0:01:46.920
Ihama yenyoka.

0:01:46.920,0:01:47.960
Hongu.

0:01:47.960,0:01:52.220
Isu tiri vanhu vatatu maari nokuti murume uyu ane simba kwazvo,

0:01:52.220,0:01:56.800
simba rakanyanyisa uye hukuru kwazvo mu humambo hwe mweya.

0:01:56.800,0:02:04.100
Iwe unogona kunge uchimuona semudiki, muduku, se munhuwo zvake uye mukomana anozvininipisa

0:02:04.100,0:02:12.100
asi muhumambo hwe mweya, paanozarura muromo wake kurumbidza Mwari kana kunyengetera,

0:02:12.100,0:02:16.220
umambo hwedu hunotyisidzirwa zvikuru.

0:02:16.220,0:02:22.080
Chakavanzika chipi nechipi munyika muno chinoratidzwa.

0:02:22.080,0:02:30.040
Ndokusaka takapinda maari kuti tinyaradze ramangwana rake

0:02:30.040,0:02:40.680
asi minyengetero yose yamai vake vanodikanwa inoramba ichimuponesa nguva yose. Waona?

0:02:40.680,0:02:49.580
Handizivi kuti chii chiri kundiita kuti nditaure izvi asi ini ndiri pasi pesimba randisingagone kunzwisisa.

0:02:49.580,0:02:53.800
Riri kundiita kuti ndireurure; Ndichazvitaura.

0:02:53.800,0:02:57.840
Kare...

0:02:57.840,0:03:01.960
Tenzi wedu achandiuraya asi ini handigone kuzvidzora.

0:03:01.960,0:03:04.540
Ndianiko tenzi akutuma?

0:03:04.540,0:03:07.160
Ndapota musandiita kuti nditaure zita rake.

0:03:07.160,0:03:08.860
Taura! ita izvozvo - taura!

0:03:08.860,0:03:19.720
Ndi Baphomet. Iye ndi mwari wechihedheni uyo Akarurama Akavhara zvibayiro

0:03:19.720,0:03:26.520
ne kurumbidza kwaifanirwa kuitwa pachena.

0:03:26.520,0:03:31.100
Akarurama Akauya panyika ino ndokumuparadza

0:03:31.100,0:03:44.720
saka iyezvino tenzi wedu anongogamuchira rumbidzo yake ne chibayiro kuburikidza nemimhanzi yenyika ino.

0:03:44.720,0:03:47.780
Ndiri kukuudza. Uyu mukomana muimbi anogona chaizvo.

0:03:47.780,0:03:49.120
Iwe unoti iye ndiyani?

0:03:49.120,0:03:51.860
Iye ane matarenda akawanda.

0:03:51.860,0:03:56.880
Anogona zve ati, sayenzi; iye anogona chero chinhu.

0:03:56.880,0:04:02.380
Mimhanzi, bhora re basiketi , ingozvitaura.

0:04:02.380,0:04:07.400
Tenzi wedu akaona kuti mwoyo wake waingopindura kune Akarurama.

0:04:07.400,0:04:10.400
Mweya wake unoshuva kune Akarurama.

0:04:10.400,0:04:17.980
Tenzi wangu ndiye uyo vanhu vari mumabhizimisi emimhanzi enyika ino vanonamata.

0:04:17.980,0:04:23.680
Zvakanaka. Iwe wati "nzira" dzose idzo anogamuchira zvibayiro nadzo

0:04:23.680,0:04:25.740
dzakavharwa ne Akaruruama.

0:04:25.740,0:04:26.380
Hongu.

0:04:26.380,0:04:28.540
Uye kuti vakagadzira dzimwe nzira ...

0:04:28.540,0:04:30.680
Kuburikidza ne mumhanzi!

0:04:30.680,0:04:34.300
Zvinoreva here kuti umambo hwako hwemadhimoni hunotonga kuburikidza nemimhanzi yenyika?

0:04:34.300,0:04:35.680
Hongu.

0:04:35.680,0:04:38.020
Munogona kutiziva isu nemazita akasiyana.

0:04:38.020,0:04:43.240
Akaita seapi?

0:04:43.240,0:04:53.760
Pamusoro pezvose tine chechi yasatani, tine iruminati,

0:04:53.760,0:05:05.780
tine AMORC Rosicrucian Order uye Ku Klux Klan.

0:05:05.780,0:05:08.200
Uye iwe unoti vanhu imimi munoshanda kuburikidza nemimhanzi?

0:05:08.200,0:05:09.100
Hongu.

0:05:09.100,0:05:11.480
Ungagonona kutsanangura kuti unoshanda sei nemumhanzi?

0:05:11.480,0:05:14.920
Tinoita zviratidzo zvedu seizvi.

0:05:14.920,0:05:19.900
Pfava hako. Chokutanga chii? Chiratidzo chekutanga ...

0:05:19.900,0:05:23.060
Ita tione! Ratidza chiratidzo chekutanga. Chiratidzo chokutanga chii?

0:05:23.060,0:05:26.080
Chekutanga.

0:05:26.080,0:05:27.760
Ndiyo maitiro aunoratidza chiratidzo chekutanga here?

0:05:27.760,0:05:28.780
Hongu!

0:05:28.780,0:05:30.200
Chinomirira chii?

0:05:30.200,0:05:44.460
Iyo inzira yekupa mbiri, simba, kukudza uye pamusoro pezvose, kuvimbika,

0:05:44.460,0:05:50.380
kuna tenzi, zvichireva kuti, "ndina tenzi mumwe chete".

0:05:50.380,0:05:53.160
Kwe humambo hupi - umambo hwechiedza kana rima?

0:05:53.160,0:06:03.260
Apo ini ndinotaura nezvavana mwari vechihedheni, tinotonga kumatenga, mumhepo, nyika

0:06:03.260,0:06:07.740
ne makungwa, kunyanya rima.

0:06:07.740,0:06:08.440
Rima?

0:06:08.440,0:06:08.960
hongu.

0:06:08.960,0:06:20.540
Apo vainge vava kuda kubereka mweya uyu, takauraya vaaitedzana navo vana vakange vakaberekwa kutanga.

0:06:20.540,0:06:24.120
Amai vake vaizivikanwa kuti vaiva ngomwa.

0:06:24.120,0:06:29.920
Akauya uye tenzi wangu akatituma kuti timuuraye.

0:06:29.920,0:06:39.180
Pazuva iroro, usiku ihwohwo muchipatara, pane imwe nzvimbo mu Imo State ...

0:06:39.180,0:06:48.020
o kwete, kwete Imo State, asi pane imwe nzvimbo mu nyika ye Ibo. Ndiyo yatinoti "Arondisog".

0:06:48.020,0:06:51.500
Hongu, ndinorangarira zvakajeka kwazvo.

0:06:51.500,0:06:59.400
Takasvika usiku ihwohwo kuti timuburitse muchibereko asi Uyo Akarurama akapindira.

0:06:59.400,0:07:04.860
Iye akatibvisa. Isu takanga taoma mitezo; hatina kumuuraya.

0:07:04.860,0:07:22.120
Akazvarwa uye tenzi wedu akapika kuti isu - Leo, Morpheus naAdder -

0:07:22.120,0:07:28.600
tinofanira kuve nechokwadi chokuti mweya uyu unofa asati ava nemakore masere.

0:07:28.600,0:07:38.680
Takaedza nzira dzose asi akararama nekuda kweminyengetero yomwoyo wose yaamai vake.

0:07:38.680,0:07:46.180
Takaedza dzimwe nzira dzokumuuraya; isu takakonzeresa tsaona ne zvinetso, ingozvitaura.

0:07:46.180,0:07:53.700
Takaedza asi minyengetero yaamai vake nekurova kwe hana ye mwoyo uyu, mwoyo wake ...

0:07:53.700,0:08:03.120
Sezvamunotaura muBhaibheri, "Dhavhidhi murume wepa mwoyo waMwari". Ichokwadi.

0:08:03.120,0:08:04.860
Iwe wakati chii?

0:08:04.860,0:08:08.180
Ini ndakati, handina kundandama ...

0:08:08.180,0:08:17.420
Ndataura kuti semuBhaibheri - "Dhavhidhi murume wepa mwoyo waMwari".

0:08:17.420,0:08:24.140
Uyu mweyawo murume wemwoyo waMwari.

0:08:24.140,0:08:31.140
Haafariri zvisina maturo; haadi zvinhu zvenyama.

0:08:31.140,0:08:38.780
Anongova nerudo ku vanhu, kunyange kune avo vaasingazivi.

0:08:38.780,0:08:43.140
Chero bedzi akangoziva kuti munhu iyeye ari ane zvaanoda, anoda kubatsira.

0:08:43.140,0:08:48.740
Anechido che kugoverana chero chaanacho.

0:08:48.740,0:08:54.020
Zvakanaka, ungagone here kutiudza kuti unotonga sei nyika kuburikidza nemimhanzi yenyika? Sei?

0:08:54.020,0:09:09.480
Ndati, patinenge tichiimba, tinoshandura pfungwa ne mweya wemuviri womunhu

0:09:09.480,0:09:22.780
kuva ne zana kubva muzana ruchiva rwe zvisina maturo, mimhanzi, zvepabonde ne chero chinhu chiri chivi.

0:09:22.780,0:09:30.800
Mweya wakadaro haungambofi - sezvatiri kuita kumweya uyu - wakaverenga Shoko raMwari.

0:09:30.800,0:09:40.840
Havangagoni kunyengetera nemwoyo wose kana kushanyira imba ya Mwari zvine mutsigo.

0:09:40.840,0:09:48.480
Iwe unogara uchi ...

0:09:48.480,0:09:49.260
Ndapota!

0:09:49.260,0:09:51.500
Iwe unoda kuita chii?

0:09:51.500,0:10:06.860
Mweya unogara uchitsvaga mabhawa, makirabhu, dzimba dzeupfambi, ingozvitaura.

0:10:06.860,0:10:12.700
Chinhu chipi nechipi chine chivi asi chisina uyo Akarurama.

0:10:12.700,0:10:17.880
Kuburikidza nemumhanzi uyu unokozva mweya yevanhu kuzvinhu zve zvivi.

0:10:17.880,0:10:20.000
Hongu.

0:10:20.000,0:10:22.880
Zvinoreva here kuti iwe une nziyo idzi dzenyika?

0:10:22.880,0:10:38.540
Nziyo dzenyika idzi dzisati dzabuditswa, vanamati vedu vanopa minyengetero yedu.

0:10:38.540,0:10:42.840
Apo pavanopa minyengetero - ndezve panyama here kana kuti ndezve mweya here?

0:10:42.840,0:10:48.620
Inogara iri muimba yemukati, isina kuziviswa kumunhu.

0:10:48.620,0:10:49.300
Hazvina kuratidzwa ku munhu?

0:10:49.300,0:10:49.800
Hongu.

0:10:49.800,0:10:52.380
Kamuri yakavanzika iyi iripi?

0:10:52.380,0:10:54.380
Vari kumativi ose pasi rese.

0:10:54.380,0:10:55.260
Kwose Kwese?

0:10:55.260,0:10:56.720
Tiri kwose kwose.

0:10:56.720,0:11:03.140
Ndisu varidzi ve nyika ino asi Akarurama Anoda kuitora kubva kuna tenzi wedu.

0:11:03.140,0:11:09.020
Iye Akarurama Anoda kutora umambo hwakaipa uhu kubva kuna tenzi wako?

0:11:09.020,0:11:09.900
Hongu.

0:11:09.900,0:11:15.440
Iwe wati chero nguva mimhanzi ikabuditswa, vanhu imimi munopa munyengetero mukamuri yenyu yakavanzika.

0:11:15.440,0:11:17.740
Ungandipindura here?

0:11:17.740,0:11:21.140
Wati kudii?

0:11:21.140,0:11:22.620
Munonamata?

0:11:22.620,0:11:23.140
Hongu.

0:11:23.140,0:11:28.520
Paunopa munyengetero, munyengetero iwoyo unoitei kumimhanzi, isati yaburwa?

0:11:28.520,0:11:32.720
Haisi minyengetero nje. Zvakafanana nekupira.

0:11:32.720,0:11:33.960
Kungofanana nokupira?

0:11:33.960,0:11:34.980
Hongu.

0:11:34.980,0:11:38.260
Unoziva mutauro iwoyo here?

0:11:38.260,0:11:40.280
Handigone kuburitsa mutauro wakadaro.

0:11:40.280,0:11:43.960
Pindura - unoziva mutauro wacho here?

0:11:43.960,0:11:47.600
Hazvisi kwatiri kutaura; ndewe vanamati kuti vataure.

0:11:47.600,0:11:48.620
Vanamati ndivo vanoutaura?

0:11:48.620,0:11:55.700
Mutauro wacho wakangofanana nepurogiramu. Unotironga isu; unotipa bvumo.

0:11:55.700,0:11:56.560
Rekuitei?

0:11:56.560,0:11:58.520
Kuzviratidza mumunhu.

0:11:58.520,0:12:01.060
Ngatitii mumwe munhu ari kuteerera mimwe yemimhanzi yawapinda mairi;

0:12:01.060,0:12:03.720
chii chingaitika kune munhu iyeye apo anenge achiteerera kurwiyo racho?

0:12:03.720,0:12:04.700
Chii chaungaita?

0:12:04.700,0:12:16.060
Somuenzaniso, nokungoteerera mimhanzi wacho, hatina bvumo izere kwamuri ikoko

0:12:16.060,0:12:22.880
kusvikira tashandisa chinokonzera kuti tikurumidze kupindura.

0:12:22.880,0:12:25.820
Chii chinokurumidzisa kupindura?

0:12:25.820,0:12:36.060
Unogona kutaura nezvokunwa, mofini, herowini, kokeni kana mbanje -

0:12:36.060,0:12:44.720
chinhu chipi nechipi chinozozarura pfungwa ne kuita kuti pfungwa dzisinunguke.

0:12:44.720,0:12:52.300
iyo inodzinga Mweya wa Mwari kubva mupfungwa.

0:12:52.300,0:12:59.800
Tisati taita izvozvo, takaedza nzira dzakawanda dzekudzidzisa mweya uyu.

0:12:59.800,0:13:08.400
Kubva muna 2009/2010 mushure mekudzidza kwake kwe zve kushandira nyika kwevechidiki ,

0:13:08.400,0:13:26.380
iye akabatana nemuteveri wedu akazara uyo akanga aine matatuu pamuviri wake.

0:13:26.380,0:13:27.740
Aiva nematatuu?

0:13:27.740,0:13:40.660
Nhengo yedu yaive yakanyorwa matatuu pamafudzi kusvika kudumbu.

0:13:40.660,0:13:50.280
Akaona chiratidzo chedu icho chiri ziso ramunoona padhora rebepa,

0:13:50.280,0:13:53.940
zvakangofanana nemapiramidhi mumazuva ekare.

0:13:53.940,0:13:57.120
Paakasangana ne nhengo yako izere chii chakaitika kwaari?

0:13:57.120,0:14:05.960
Akanga achifanirwa kunge ari munhu chaiye weku gamuchira Damien munyika ino.

0:14:05.960,0:14:08.680
Damien ndiani?

0:14:08.680,0:14:19.780
Damien anozivikanwa zvikuru munyika ino. Chiratidzo chake ndeche 666.

0:14:19.780,0:14:20.600
Hongu.

0:14:20.600,0:14:25.300
Vanhu vangani vawakagara kuburikidza nemimhanzi munyika ino?

0:14:25.300,0:14:28.940
Mabhiriyoni, ziriyoni, havaverengeke.

0:14:28.940,0:14:29.560
Havaverengeke?

0:14:29.560,0:14:31.240
Zvisingaverengeke?

0:14:31.240,0:14:34.120
Chii chiri kuitika kumararamiro avo zvino?

0:14:34.120,0:14:39.540
Pavanoenda kuchechi, vanonzwa Shoko ra Mwari, ehe

0:14:39.540,0:14:46.240
saka isu tiri kunanikidzwa kumhanyira kunze kunovamirira.

0:14:46.240,0:14:56.720
Pavanobuda, nekuda kwetsika yavo inova ndiyo inovakonzeresa, tinodzoka.

0:14:56.720,0:14:59.180
Unoitei kune hupenyu hwavo paunodzoka?

0:14:59.180,0:15:04.580
Tinoita zvakatonyanya kudarika kare; tinoparadza zvose.

0:15:04.580,0:15:07.680
Iwe wati avo vanoteerera mimhanzi yenyu yepanyika yamunayo,

0:15:07.680,0:15:09.700
havana nguva ya Mwari.

0:15:09.700,0:15:10.620
Hongu!

0:15:10.620,0:15:14.660
Unosiyanisa sei vanhu ivavo kubva kuvana vaMwari chaivo?

0:15:14.660,0:15:22.600
Zviri nyore. Tinoziva kuburikidza nezvavanotora. Doro rimwe razvavanotora.

0:15:22.600,0:15:26.260
Ndeupi musiyano pakati pevanhu ivavo nevana va Mwari?

0:15:26.260,0:15:36.500
Vanhu ivavo vakaita semidziyo kwatiri; midziyo yatinayo.

0:15:36.500,0:15:38.120
Avo vanotora zvinokurudzira?

0:15:38.120,0:15:40.280
Hongu.

0:15:40.280,0:15:41.440
Ivo midziyo.

0:15:41.440,0:15:45.920
Vanhu imimi munogona here kugara muvana va Mwari kuburikidza nemumhanzi uyu wenyika? Zvinoita here?

0:15:45.920,0:15:48.300
Aiwa, nokuti havashandisi zvinokonzeresa.

0:15:48.300,0:15:50.620
Zvinokurudzira izvozvo zvinokubatsira kuti upinde mavari here?

0:15:50.620,0:15:51.540
Hongu.

0:15:51.540,0:15:52.680
Ndeavo vanoshandisa chete ...

0:15:52.680,0:15:53.740
Ndiyo rezinesi yedu.

0:15:53.740,0:15:54.400
Ndiyo rezinesi yako?

0:15:54.400,0:15:56.240
Hungu - yekupinda nayo.

0:15:56.240,0:15:56.980
yekupinda nayo.

0:15:56.980,0:15:57.780
Hongu.

0:15:57.780,0:16:01.200
Wakapinda sei mumuviri uyu? Panofanira kuva nenzira. Zviri kuburikidza ne rukurudziro here?

0:16:01.200,0:16:03.000
Iwe wakagara mumuviri uyu sei?

0:16:03.000,0:16:12.180
Akasumwa kwazviri ne chinokurudzira paakanga ari kuchikoro.

0:16:12.180,0:16:23.620
Muzukuru wake  uyo anoita zve mashiripiti akaedza kumudzidzisa.

0:16:23.620,0:16:28.700
